description:
This is a 27 minute workout called 'How to Get Flexible Part 2 - The 20 Min Guided Stretch Routine | Day 12' from the channel Yoga With Tim.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Stretching and Flexibility/Yoga.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Part 2 of the full body stretch routine with warm-up integrated. This gets more into the science and methodology of creating better mobility for the body. If you would like to get more yoga in for the day, you are welcome to practice any of the previous classes before this one....
